name: SparseFactorization_t
desc: Constants that define the factorization type.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationCholesky: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents Cholesky (LLᵀ) factorization.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationLDLT: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents the default LDLᵀ factorization.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationLDLTUnpivoted: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents Cholesky-like LDLᵀ factorization with only one-by-one pivots and no pivoting.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationLDLTSBK: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents LDLᵀ factorization with Supernode-Bunch-Kaufman and static pivoting.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationLDLTTPP: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents LDLᵀ factorization with full-threshold partial pivoting.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationQR: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents QR factorization.

items.name: var SparseFactorizationCholeskyAtA: SparseFactorization_t
items.desc: A constant that represents QR factorization without storing Q.
